{"tid":218412,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[bafs] paper2b/商管 心得","createTime":"2017-04-26T13:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T22:01:16.000Z","uid":9187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eba4506eff2074941f2dacd74f09002c94b4dea0","tid":218412,"uid":9187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:09:33.000Z","msg":"相信大部分嘅bafs考生都會揀accting(2A),但對於數底差嘅 2B係你嘅必然選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多人都會話2B好多野背 好辛苦 但有留意pp嘅就會知道d題目成日翻炒<br />\n<br />\n1)背係背d好general嘅野 要識得apply落given case<br />\n<br />\nEg. 2015 SQ Q2 <br />\nRisk management strategies in case of shoplifting<br />\n1) concept位: risk management strategies<br />\n2) scenario/case: shoplifting (+eg)<br />\n<br />\n你唔可以話答完個4種strategies就得<br />\n理想答法<br />\n-risk transfer <br />\n-For example: insurance+elab <br />\n-elab係要同shoplifting有關<br />\n<br />\n2) 背係背pt elab就自己諗<br />\n<br />\n題目given caae唔同 書入面嘅elab就冇用 要適得零活變通<br />\n<br />\n3) 一定要操pp<br />\n題目經常翻炒 eg customer buying process <br />\nDse咁多年出咗3次<br />\nPp priority : dse&gt;al<br />\nAL d題目可以睇下 因為會翻炒<br />\nEg 2011 essay=2016 essay (hrm)<br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到商管人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9462b27b76851c3b2b5e3278878b3bd9b7d65084","tid":218412,"uid":9187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:22:49.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbed6a5c14801697460b9e32305826b8a6eb12c","tid":218412,"uid":9187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T15:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac3cec8ca468196d4745a63ba8d0b82864c0457","tid":218412,"uid":68014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:25:21.000Z","msg":"支持敏兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n商管人表示，你要攞高分，首先要食晒d書入腦先，無背書，什麼都不是"},{"p